1.title: Clip: Jay's Lightning Jet

episode of.title: Clip: Lego Set Builds Ninjago - Artifex (TV Series 2016– )

1.plot: Save Ed and Edna from the shark army's crab with Jay's Lightning Jet in this thrilling The Lego Ninjago Movie set. The jet has a handle for easy pick-up-and-play and maximum swooshability, plus an opening minifigure cockpit, spring-loaded shooter and trigger-activated rotating electro-disc. Lego 70614.

2.title: Clip: Kai's Fire Mech

episode of.title: Clip: Lego Set Builds Ninjago - Artifex (TV Series 2016– )

2.plot: Get set for sizzling battle action with this huge and highly posable The Lego Ninjago Movie mech. The Fire Mech features an opening minifigure cockpit, 2 shoulder disc shooters and 2 arms with non-shooting fire blasters. Includes 6 minifigures with assorted weapons-including Kai's katanas and Zane's bow and arrow-to offer even more thrilling role-play possibilities. Lego 70615.

3.title: Clip: Zane's Ice Tank

episode of.title: Clip: Lego Set Builds Ninjago - Artifex (TV Series 2016– )

3.plot: Help Zane save Patty Keys and Torben from the shark soldiers with this action-packed The Lego Ninjago Movie Ice Tank set. This cool vehicle features an opening minifigure cockpit, big tracks, ice cannon with 6-stud rapid shooter, and a rotating ice container. Lego 70616.

4.title: Clip: Temple of the Ultimate Ultimate Weapon

episode of.title: Clip: Lego Set Builds Ninjago - Artifex (TV Series 2016– )

4.plot: Join a ninja mission to infiltrate The Lego Ninjago Movie Temple of The Ultimate Ultimate Weapon. The temple features a secret entrance, trapdoor, rock-dropping and dynamite-dropping functions, blade-shooting and chopping-sword traps, dungeon, a hanging cage to capture a minifigure inside, and a pull-out section with poles for minifigures to leap between to reach the treasure chest. Lego 70617.

5.title: Clip: Destiny's Bounty

episode of.title: Clip: Lego Set Builds Ninjago - Artifex (TV Series 2016– )

5.plot: Construct Wu's huge ninja training base, Destiny's Bounty. This highly detailed The Lego Ninjago Movie model consists of 3 modular levels and features a double-headed dragon figurehead, decorated sails, wind-up-and-release anchors, dojo area for ninja training, a bathroom and Wu's bedroom in the hull. This amazing model also includes hidden weapons including the ultimate weapon. Lego 70618.

6.title: Clip: Ninjago City

episode of.title: Clip: Lego Set Builds Ninjago - Artifex (TV Series 2016– )

6.plot: Live the life of a ninja in Ninjago City. Features a 3-level model (each level lifts off for easy play) connected by a sliding elevator, plus a traditional fishing boat and includes 16 minifigures. Lego 70620.

7.title: Clip: Lloyd Spinjitzu Master

episode of.title: Clip: Lego Set Builds Ninjago - Artifex (TV Series 2016– )

7.plot: Learn all the skills of Spinjitzu with Lloyd. Featuring a Spinjitzu spinner with buildable Lego brick handle, spinner element with minifigure capsule and a rip cord. Learn different minifigure-spinning, rolling and jumping techniques and even tougher skills using the included weapon rack as an obstacle. Includes a Lloyd minifigure with 2 shurikens to hold in the spinner. Lego 70628.

8.title: Clip: Piranha Attack

episode of.title: Clip: Lego Set Builds Ninjago - Artifex (TV Series 2016– )

8.plot: Play out an action-packed Piranha Mech pursuit of a rickshaw through NINJAGO City with THE LEGO NINJAGO MOVIE Piranha Attack set. The Piranha Mech features opening jaws with a minifigure cockpit inside, plus 2 flick missiles. Lego 70629.

9.title: Clip: Garmadon's Volcano Lair

episode of.title: Clip: Lego Set Builds Ninjago - Artifex (TV Series 2016– )

9.plot: Join Zane's mission to infiltrate evil Garmadon's Volcano Lair and take on the shark army, with this exciting set. The base includes a minifigure-launch function at the tip of the volcano, Garmadon's throne room, computer lab with a mini piranha mech prototype, construction zone with an exploding wall function and rotating crane to lift the included shark figure. Lego 70631.

10.title: Clip: Quake Mech

episode of.title: Clip: Lego Set Builds Ninjago - Artifex (TV Series 2016– )

10.plot: Fire 'soundwaves' from Cole's Quake Mech to save TV reporter Fred Finley from the shark army, with this all-action set. The highly posable, uni-wheel Quake Mech features an opening minifigure cockpit, fold-up shoulder 'loudspeakers' with 8 hidden 'soundwave'-shooting flick missiles, fully posable arms with gripping fists and a big wheel with stabilizer. Lego 70632.

11.title: Clip: Garmadon, Garmadon, Garmadon!

episode of.title: Clip: Lego Set Builds Ninjago - Artifex (TV Series 2016– )

11.plot: Help Lloyd to save Nomis and Nancy from Garmadon's Shark Mech with this action-packed Garmadon, Garmadon, Garmadon! set. The mech features 2 opening cockpits, Lego studs to stand the Garmadon minifigure on top of the shark's head, trigger-operated snapping jaws, posable legs and 2 shooting cannons. Lego 70656.

20.title: Clip: Spinjitzu Training

episode of.title: Clip: Lego Set Builds Ninjago - Artifex (TV Series 2016– )

20.plot: Join the ninja heroes at the dojo with this action-packed The Lego Ninjago Movie Spinjitzu Training set, featuring a dojo wall with a scroll and 2 detachable staffs, weapon rack with 2 detachable katanas, combat training station, Garmadon combat dummy, plus 2 mini figures. Lego 70606.

21.title: Clip: Ninjago City Chase

episode of.title: Clip: Lego Set Builds Ninjago - Artifex (TV Series 2016– )

21.plot: Team up with Lloyd Garmadon, Nya and Officer Toque to prevent Shark Army Thug robbing a street food stall vendor in Ninjago City Chase. This exciting The Lego Ninjago Movie set features a 3-wheel police tuc-tuc vehicle, street food stall with assorted food elements, plus 2 lampposts with a connecting chain of festive Ninjago lanterns. Lego 70607.

22.title: Clip: Manta Ray Bomber

episode of.title: Clip: Lego Set Builds Ninjago - Artifex (TV Series 2016– )

22.plot: Help Cole save Shen-Li in this cool The Lego Ninjago Movie set, featuring the Manta Ray Bomber with 2 spring-loaded shooters, 2 bomb elements and a detachable boat. Includes 4 mini figures with assorted weapons and accessories to ramp up the role-play action possibilities. Lego 70609.

23.title: Clip: Flying Jelly Sub

episode of.title: Clip: Lego Set Builds Ninjago - Artifex (TV Series 2016– )

23.plot: Join ninja Jay in battle against the shark army and protect Takuma's boat from Flying Jelly Sub attacks, in this action-packed The Lego Ninjago Movie set. The sub features an opening minifigure cockpit, rotating legs, 2 flick missiles and swinging 'toxic' tentacles. Also includes a boat, plus 4 minifigures with assorted weapons to add to the battle role-play options. Lego 70610.

24.title: Clip: Movie Making Kit

episode of.title: Clip: Lego Set Builds Ninjago - Artifex (TV Series 2016– )

24.plot: Create thrilling scenes with the Ninjago Movie Making Kit, featuring a double-sided cardboard backdrop with alternate scenes on each side, buildable LEGO scenery, camera rig to hold a smartphone (not included) and a Kai minifigure with assorted props. Lego 853702.

27.title: Clip: Master Falls

episode of.title: Clip: Lego Set Builds Ninjago - Artifex (TV Series 2016– )

27.plot: Team up with Wu and Kai to take on Jungle Garmadon in this awesome The Lego Ninjago Movie Master Falls set. The jungle bridge features an opening cage and a hidden cave with a skeleton inside holding a secret map. Also includes 3 minifigures with assorted weapons-including Wu's staff and 4-armed Jungle Garmadon's 4 swords-to bolster the role-play action. Lego 70608.

28.title: Clip: Nya's Water Strider

episode of.title: Clip: Lego Set Builds Ninjago - Artifex (TV Series 2016– )

28.plot: Launch into battle against the shark army and pretend to walk on water and climb walls with this awesome The Lego Ninjago Movie mech. The Water Strider features a 360-degree rotating minifigure cockpit, 6-stud rapid shooter and 4 posable legs and feet to create powerful battle poses. Lego 70611.

29.title: Clip: Green Ninja Mech Dragon

episode of.title: Clip: Lego Set Builds Ninjago - Artifex (TV Series 2016– )

29.plot: Outwit The Green Ninja's evil father Garmadon with this mighty THE LEGO NINJAGO MOVIE mech. The Green Ninja Mech Dragon features articulated snapping jaws, a fully posable body, wheel-activated swooshing tail, 2 leg-mounted stud shooters and 2 hidden pop-out thrusters. Lego 70612.

30.title: Clip: Garma Mecha Man

episode of.title: Clip: Lego Set Builds Ninjago - Artifex (TV Series 2016– )

30.plot: Help Lloyd protect civilian Pat from attack by Garma Mecha Man with this awesome THE LEGO NINJAGO MOVIE set. This huge and highly posable mech features an opening minifigure cockpit for Garmadon, spring-loaded shark blaster, ammo belt and a fish tank. Lego 70613.

imdb.plot outline: Lego Ninjago is an exciting world of ninjas battling against the forces of evil. Your child will enjoy meeting their heroes and role-playing their exciting and varied adventures. In addition, they can play out the hit Tv series and play against their friends in a battle to become the Master of Spinjitzu.
